# Dataset Description

## Table customers
**Description:**
Contains information about customers.
Each customer has a unique customer_id and is associated with orders.

**Fields:**
| Field          | Description               |
| -------------- | ------------------------  |
| customer_id    | customer identification   |
| customer_city  | city                      |
| customer_state | state                     |

## Table geolocation
**Description:**
Contains information about the geographical location of Brazil's postal codes

**Fields:**
| Field | Description |
|------|----------|
| geolocation_zip_code_prefix | The first digits of the zip code |
| geolocation_lat | Geographical latitude |
| geolocation_lng | Geographical longitude |
| geolocation_city | City |
| geolocation_state | State |

## Table order_items
**Description:**
Contains information about the products included in each order
One order can contain multiple items.

**Fields:**
| Field | Description |
|------|----------|
| order_id | Order identificator |
| order_item_id | Serial number of the product inside the order |
| product_id | Product identificator |
| seller_id | Seller identificator |
| shipping_limit_date | Deadline for sending |
| price | Cost of the product |
| freight_value | Shipping cost |

## Table order_payments
**Description:**
Contains information about the payment of orders.
One order can have multiple payments.

**Fields:**
| Field | Description |
|------|----------|
| order_id | Order identificator |
| payment_sequential | Payment number inside the order |
| payment_type | Payment method |
| payment_installments | Number of payments (installments) |
| payment_value | Payment amount |

## Table orders
**Description:**
The main table of the project.
Each record corresponds to one order.

**Fields:**
| Field | Description |
|------|----------|
| order_id | Order identificator |
| customer_id | Customer identificator |
| order_status | Status of order |
| order_purchase_timestamp | Date and time of placing the order |
| order_approved_at | Order confirmation date |
| order_delivered_carrier_date | Date of transfer of the order to the carrier |
| order_delivered_customer_date | Delivery date to the buyer |
| order_estimated_delivery_date | Planned delivery date |

## Table products
**Description:**
Contains information about the products

**Fields:**
| Field | Description |
|------|----------|
| product_id | Product identificator |
| product_category_name | Product category |
| product_name_lenght | Length of the product name |
| product_description_lenght | Length of the product description |
| product_photos_qty | Number of photos |
| product_weight_g | Product weight (g) |
| product_length_cm | Product Length (cm) |
| product_height_cm | Product height (cm) |
| product_width_cm | Product width (cm) |

## Table sellers
**Description:**
Contains information about the sellers of the marketplace

**Fields:**
| Field | Description |
|------|----------|
| seller_id | Seller identificator |
| seller_zip_code_prefix | The first digits of the zip code |
| seller_city | Seller's city |
| seller_state | Seller's state |

## Table product_category_name_translation
**Description:**
Contains a translation of product categories from Portuguese into English

**Fields:**
| Field | Description |
|------|----------|
| product_category_name | Category name in Portuguese |
| product_category_name_english | Category name in English |